{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "舞台上的怪物人偶第3话 排演三人行",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "演出准备井然有序地进行着。\\n莱姬希在这一过程中意识到\\n“只要用心去做，心就能体现在成果上”。\\n然而就在剧本完成在即之时，梅洛的妹妹\\n却病情告危，演出陷入了困境。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "施密特你爱的是卡萝尔，\\n我的身体不过是承载\\n卡萝尔的心的容器。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "而容器中诞生的我的意识，\\n不过是卡萝尔的心的赝品。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "我不过是个只会嫉妒又有缺陷的人偶。\\n与其夹在你们中间让你烦恼，\\n我还不如消失了好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "等等，你等等，弗兰。\\n你不是什么赝品。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "是我太过任性……\\n企图让死去的卡萝尔复活……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "好，可以了。\\n二位排练辛苦了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "唔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "（虽然早就料到了……\\n但演戏还是真是难啊。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "（明明莱姬希已经有很大的进步，\\n我却还是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "梅洛，我对剧本有意见。\\n要求改写。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "嚯，这语气就像是大明星一样啊……\\n说来听听，哪里不满意？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "弗兰是人偶，\\n不可能懂得那么多感情都叫什么。\\n“只会嫉妒”这种台词很不自然。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "唔……的确有道理。\\n那我改掉吧。莱姬希，多谢你\\n能从人偶的角度提供意见。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "（原来如此……莱姬希在弗兰身上\\n找到了自己的影子。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "（那我也找一找自己和施密特的\\n相同之处并以此为出发点就好了。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "加斯特，你能试试下场戏吗？\\n你的独角戏那一场。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "嗯，好的。没问题。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "我埋头于各种研究。研究那些\\n能起死回生、治愈百病的灵药……\\n试遍了能拯救卡萝尔的所有方法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "然而……然而我是从何时起……\\n误入歧途的呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "当初我明明只是想救她。\\n救回那个在痛苦中死去的……\\n我深爱的卡萝尔。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "（嚯……加斯特的演技\\n开始变好了啊。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "（果然拜托他\\n演这个角色的决定没错。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "呵呵呵……刚才的排练，梅洛和\\n加斯特的眼神中都充满了神采呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——予以赞同。梅洛的剧本\\n也写得很顺利。而且……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "我越来越能够从这部戏中\\n感受到“心”的存在了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——嗯，我也隐约能够理解。\\n故事在融入了莱姬希和加斯特的\\n意见之后正不断变得生动起来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "这正是大家用心去做的结果吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——用心……无法理解。\\n——诶？无法理解吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——予以肯定。所谓心，\\n只是维持身体机能\\n和处理交流信息的器官而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "人类的大脑虽说在形态和性质上\\n与我们的“心”有所不同，\\n但应该起着相同的作用。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "不过，心真是不可思议。它不单纯\\n是一个器官。只要人们用心去做，\\n它就能体现在成果上……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "它是无形的，\\n也不是只要有材料就能造出来的。\\n我终于……明白了这一点。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——是啊。人偶的创造者们之所以\\n给自我系统命名为“心”，是否也是\\n因为经历了如此复杂的创造过程呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "而创造了我们的麦斯特罗也……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——这就不知道了。但是，这部戏的\\n创造者梅洛在看到演出成功之时，\\n会露出怎样的表情呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "这正是我现在最想看到的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "也许看了以后就能明白\\n麦斯特罗当初是以什么样的心情\\n把我们造出来的了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——呵呵，剧本也即将完成了。\\n真让人期待啊！\\n——予以肯定。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "莱姬希！久等了。\\n今天可以收工了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——诶？这就收工了吗？\\n——太阳还没落山呢，为什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "剧本已经到收尾阶段了，\\n我打算今晚一口气把剩下的部分完成。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "是吗，终于要完成了啊……\\n好期待明天的到来啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "嗯，敬请期待。\\n明天排练的时候我会带去的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "呼……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "（故事也到了最关键的时刻，\\n剩下的内容应该能\\n赶在天亮前写完……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "梅洛！梅洛！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "嗯？这么晚了，什么事啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "哈啊，哈啊……啊，梅洛，\\n幸好你在……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "你不是……医院的人吗！？\\n这深更半夜的，怎么了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "医院的使者",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……就是……\\n雪莉她……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "雪莉……她怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "无法理解……梅洛没来。\\n——好奇怪啊，已经要中午了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "这可怎么办……梅洛不来的话，\\n也没法排练。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——我去他家看看情况。\\n要是在睡大觉我可决不轻饶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "嗯，那我们一起去找他吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "没有反应……不在家？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "予以否定。发现行为个体，\\n人在里面。\\n——梅洛为什么不出来呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——开始闯入。\\n——诶？哇，等下！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "莱、莱姬希真的破门而入了……\\n呜呜……对不起了。\\n——我们进去吧，加斯特。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "梅洛！喂，你今天怎么回事啊？\\n剧本呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "剧……本？\\n剧本啊，没写完。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "什么……你说没写完……\\n你昨天不是说了会写完吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "梅洛？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "……\\n昨晚医院派人来了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "说是雪莉病危，\\n能不能活下去就看这几天了。\\n还说她能挺过去的希望……非常渺茫。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希&加斯特",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "我是为了让她重拾笑容\\n才坚持到这一步的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "然而……\\n她却要离开了……\\n我……我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——梅洛，你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "等等，莱姬希。\\n现在就让他一个人静静吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "加斯特，梅洛已经不会再\\n继续写那个剧本了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "那家伙为这场演出那么拼命，\\n全都是为了妹妹。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "如果这个愿望无法实现的话……就……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "是吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "剧场老板",
            "context": "你、你们在这里啊，不得了了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "剧场老板，发生什么事了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "剧场老板",
            "context": "梅洛联系我了！\\n他说他要辞任，不写剧本了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "梅洛……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0079",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "剧场老板",
            "context": "啊啊，怎么办！这样一来\\n就赶不上万圣节演出了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0080",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "剧场老板",
            "context": "他的一些剧本还是很卖座的，\\n我是看在这个份上才等到\\n今天……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0081",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "剧场老板",
            "context": "但是这次已经没戏了。\\n只能取消演出了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0082",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "取消……演出？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_03_0083",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}